        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "On motion that the House instruct conferees Failed by the Yeas and Nays: 211 - 213 (Roll no. 263). (consideration: CR H4249)",
        "type": "ResolvingDifferences"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2025-09-10",
        "actionTime": "18:25:47",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "POSTPONED PROCEEDINGS - At the conclusion of debate on the DeLauro motion to instruct conferees on H.R. 3944, the Chair put the question on motion to instruct conferees and by voice vote, announced the noes had prevailed. Ms. DeLauro demanded the yeas and nays and the Chair postponed further proceedings until a time to be announced.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H41400",
        "actionDate": "2025-09-10",
        "actionTime": "18:25:37",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "The previous question was ordered without objection.",
        "type": "ResolvingDifferences"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2025-09-10",
        "actionTime": "18:06:20",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "DEBATE - The House proceeded with one hour of debate on the DeLauro motion to instruct conferees.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H40150",
        "actionDate": "2025-09-10",
        "actionTime": "18:06:02",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Ms. DeLauro moved that the House instruct conferees.",
        "type": "ResolvingDifferences"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H41610",
        "actionDate": "2025-09-10",
        "actionTime": "18:02:52",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "On motion that the House disagree to the Senate amendment, and request a conference Agreed to by voice vote.",
        "type": "ResolvingDifferences"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H41400",
        "actionDate": "2025-09-10",
        "actionTime": "18:02:46",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "The previous question was ordered without objection.",
        "type": "ResolvingDifferences"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H40150",
        "actionDate": "2025-09-10",
        "actionTime": "18:02:10",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Mr. Cole moved that the House disagree to the Senate amendment, and request a conference.",
        "type": "ResolvingDifferences"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2025-09-10",
        "actionTime": "18:02:05",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Mr. Cole moved to take from the Speaker's table the bill H.R. 3944, with the Senate amendment thereto, disagree to the Senate amendment and request a conference.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionDate": "2025-08-08",
